result.name: High quality variant calls from multiple horse genome project -Run1
result.description: High quality variant discovery using multiple horse breeds - Run1. It started in spring of 2012 and is based at University of Bern,Switzerland. The project Coordinator is Prof. Tosso Leeb from the Institute of Genetics University of Bern.
result.platform: Illumina HiSeq 2500, Illumina HiSeq 3500, Illumina NovaSeq 6000
